{"tid":1346283,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚仲去元朗？不如去警總？","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T04:07:37.000Z","uid":228294,"like":3,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71d98185dd425851f0cead3bea369ff519f832ca","tid":1346283,"uid":228294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"今日返工好多淺黃淺藍都因為元朗單野動搖，好多香港人都好嬲，我地要好好運用佢地呢刻嘅嬲<br />\n但如果我地踩入元朗，只會幫港共實行「民眾內鬥」嘅策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我地要對準政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地警總集會，唔會俾人打，堅持五大訴求<br />\n針對721元朗警黑合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>今晚8點警總集合，好嗎？</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今晚見=<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去警總無用=<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca7f1cff18e8f896018e05c4019aaaa7432874f","tid":1346283,"uid":228294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d850b94d83087da296f4c58751f21cdc0459e8fe","tid":1346283,"uid":228294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497089cf0e6cd8d9f04363cb939c19449bc59e4a","tid":1346283,"uid":228294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:54:16.000Z","msg":"求集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6809e39095d10563d7805e08cd4594fa39c8e967","tid":1346283,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:54:48.000Z","msg":"又落閘law,之後又拉你"},{"pid":"a5e65a1b0d277